{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282790/extras/title_showcase.gif?t=1738578307\" /><strong>About RIFTSTORM</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">RIFTSTORM puts players into the shoes of Mythic Protocol Weavers, secret agents charged with the defense of our world from mythic threats.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282790/extras/FTUE-Sequence-6.gif?t=1738578307\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Looter-Shooter ARPG + Roguelite</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Complete missions, gather loot, and react to in-mission upgrades to create unique builds. No two missions are alike as RIFTSTORM presents a unique blend of looter-shooter action and roguelite gameplay that empowers player creativity and skill. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282790/extras/coop_gameplay_1.gif?t=1738578307\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Cooperative Multiplayer</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Invite up to two friends and tackle missions around the globe in thrilling co-op gameplay. Each Weaver presents unique gameplay mechanics and weaponry, combine their skills and powers to overcome new challenges. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282790/extras/variety_of_bosses.gif?t=1738578307\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Cosmic Techno Thriller</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enter the world of the Occultical, where secret societies and operatives exist alongside mythic threats from across the cosmos. Dive into the mysteries of the unknown and explore your place within the secretive ranks of the Mythic Protocol.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/s